- Build FFmpeg for android -

- Create standalone android ndk toolchain for android-8 platform
  How to? Read android ndk document "STANDALONE-TOOLCHAIN.html"

- Change ANDROID_ROOT in "config.sh" to your standalone toolchain folder

- Create new temp folder
  "c:/ffmpegtmp"

- Configure~!
  ./config.sh

- Edit config files
  Find "#define restrict restrict" in config.h, and change it to "#define restrict"

- Build FFmpeg using ndk-build command
